![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9e8ee4a9-cb4c-469e-9136-8f29b95e9a44/20240918_190657.jpg)

WILL OSPREAY, KYLE FLETCHER AND KONOSUKE TAKESHITA DEF. THE ELITE

What a fun main event. Kyle Fletcher pins Matt Jackson after hitting his Aussie Open finisher with Will Ospreay.

After the match, Ospreay and Takeshita start to argue but they don't get physical at the request of Don Callis